title: Bug Swarm Flies In My Mouth & Up My Nose While Hiking The Wallowa Lake Tramway. Mousetrap Monday

media:group.media:title: Bug Swarm Flies In My Mouth & Up My Nose While Hiking The Wallowa Lake Tramway. Mousetrap Monday
media:group.media:description: In this video my family enjoys a hike at the top of Mt. Howard after riding the Wallowa Lake Tramway - The steepest Gondola in the country. The trip was ruined by swarming insects that were constantly flying up my nose and in my mouth.
